Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: O.J.Simpson, sports star
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bxxf
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 3 Jun 1979
The 20,000-to-1 chance of becoming a black sports star like O.J.Simpson. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.